doesn't intend to impose onerous

05:08.266 --> 05:13.266 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
regulatory burdens
on either for-profit
colleges or other types of
colleges, as well as the

05:14.133 --> 05:15.666 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
student loan industry as well.

